* Nullability\nChecks
** Pipeline Expectations
*** Python
****_ @dp.expect_or_drop decorator
****_ SQL Boolean expression
****_ Per-column validation
*** SQL
****_ CONSTRAINT clause
****_ ON VIOLATION DROP ROW
****_ STREAMING TABLE definition
** Delta Lake Constraints
***_ NOT NULL in CREATE TABLE
***_ ALTER TABLE ALTER COLUMN
***_ Verified at write time
** Important Note
***_ Existing rows validated
***_ ALTER fails if nulls exist
***_ Plan migration carefully
